      • Movie

        public Movie​(String title,
             MovieStatusType status,
             String synopsis,
             String director,
             ArrayList<String> cast,
             MovieType type,
             LocalDateTime endOfShowingDate)
        Creates a new Movie listing, with information keyed in by the Admin.
        Parameters:
        title - Title of the new Movie.
        status - Status of the new Movie (ie. COMING_SOON, PREVIEW, NOW_SHOWING, END_OF_SHOWING).
        synopsis - Synopsis of what this new Movie is about.
        director - Name of the director of the new Movie.
        cast - List of the names of the cast members.
        type - Type of the new Movie (ie. REGULAR, 3D, BLOCKBUSTER).
        endOfShowingDate - Date and Time when the new Movie stops airing.
